tweet_text: “We must see that our troops, veterans & their families have the support they need. Together, I know we can get the job done.” #CMFCSummit

name: Sanford Bishop, Jr.
tweet_text: “I look forward to continuing the work of the Military Family Caucus & other 85 Members of Congress who make up this Caucus.” #CMFCSummit

name: Sanford Bishop, Jr.
tweet_text: “These families are impacted in countless ways – seen and unseen – and we have an obligation to do right by them.” #CMFCSummit

name: Sanford Bishop, Jr.
tweet_text: “We cannot forget the families they leave behind sacrifice just as much as our heroes who deploy on missions for our country.” #CMFCSummit

name: Sanford Bishop, Jr.

name: Sanford Bishop, Jr.
tweet_text: “Whenever I meet with military families, two people who frequently come to mind are my father-in-law and my wife.” #CMFCSummit

name: Sanford Bishop, Jr.
tweet_text: “The stories you share & input you provide help us work together to improve your quality of life & expand your opportunities.” #CMFCSummit

name: Sanford Bishop, Jr.
tweet_text: “The issues discussed today are issues we will take back to Washington with us because they are of national importance.” #CMFCSummit
